{
  "stem": "22910.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, this is very strange now and here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this is how it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it immediately started, where all Jews have to give up their businesses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No more Jews in business.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And no more Jews can get licenses for like shoemakers, and even artisans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And each day, there was a different law.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Each day?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Almost.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, you-- you felt like it was each day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It probably wasn't each day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they started a new school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, actually, they put us into the Hungarian school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we finished the year in a Hungarian school, the regular one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they separated us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Also in a Hungarian school, but the Jewish children were separate, where the Czech school use to be.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's where I-- I finished elementary school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Through 8th grade.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now in 1941, the Hungarians decided that Jews have to prove their citizenship, that they were-- you know, that they belong there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, my family-- I found out after, I knew that my family came with the Mayflower, [LAUGHS] so to speak, to that town.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They started-- they came in 1709.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I read a book.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's a new book now, which was written by some people in my area, and this is what it said, and I recognize all the names.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe from-- I don't know from where.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my family was the important family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Anyway, they-- they were the first Jews in that town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So is this it for this tape?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If I-- all right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, like in this book, which I have read just a few years ago, it mentions all the names, which are familiar to me, because they repeat first names.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, last names remain the same.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
